casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Leo Arthur FIELD, II, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157105
COA: 339526 Supreme Court of Michigan. May 30, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 11, 2017 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
